/* i really want this to be global */ /* * match url: * ^((?!job.*configure|.*Monitor/$|.*detail.*pipeline|.*api|.*replay).)*$ */ /* kbd, pre, code: HTML tag. E.g.: , 

   	pre *, code *, div.line-numbers, div.code : HTML TAG with Class. E.g.: 
; 

	.line, .line-number, .monospaced: Specified Class Name.
*/
span.vsts-build-log,        /* TFS Log Content */
div.ace_layer * {           /* Jenkins Pipeline Script Textarea*/
    font-family: "Menlo", "Ubuntu", "Ubuntu Mono", "Consolas", "Monaco" !important;
}



/*
.editor,                                    Github Codeblock
div.ace_content                     Gitlab Diff content ; Jenkins Script Box
.solarized-dark,                      http://www.myregexp.com
.js-file-line *,                            http://thisdavej.com
.changeset-message,             Jenkins Console Editor
.node-log-frame,                    Jenkins Change list
#terminal *                              Jenkins Stage View    
shellcheck
*/

/* Stylish Editor area*/
textarea,
kbd,
pre,
pre *,
code,
code *,
div.code *,
table.code,
tr.line_holder *,
.editor,
div.ace_content,
.solarized-dark,
.EnlighterJS *,
.js-file-line *,
.changeset-message,
.node-log-frame,
#terminal * {
    font-family: "Menlo" , "Andale Mono", "Ubuntu", "Ubuntu Mono", "monofur" !important;
    font-size: 15px !important;
}


/*
.editor,
div.ace_content * {
    font-family: "Ubuntu Mono" !important;
  font-size: 16px !important
}
*/
input,
select,
a.jstree-anchor,/* Artifactory Tree List */
div.line-numbers *,
.line-numbers,
.js-line-number,/* Github Codeblock */
.line,
.line-number,
.CodeMirror-line,
.gr-diff, /* Gerrit Review diff */
pre.console-output,/* Jenkins Console Output finished */
.console-output *,/* Jenkins Console Output */
.blockInner,/* Json Viewer */
.jsonpOpener,/* Json Viewer */
td.wysiwyg-macro-body *,
.timestamp {
    font-family: "Menlo", "Andale Mono", "Ubuntu", "Ubuntu Mono", "Consolas", "Monaco" !important;
/*     background-color: red; */
    font-size: 15px !important;
}





/* 	"fa":       														Gitlab
   	"octicon":  														Atom & Github
   	"win-icon": 														Microsoft
   	"icon-dropdown", "navbar-icon", "icon-home" and "icon-":         	Sonar
	"ace_":																Jenkins
    "ico":           													Sourceforge
	"pc" and "DPvwYc" and "Da":											Gmail
	"ms-Icon":															MS OneDrive
	"sort-caret":														Blackduck Hub
	"drop", "bowtie-", "view-":											TFS
	"pl-":																Github
*/

/*
Mac default fonts: , "LucidaGrande", "Kailasa", "Thonburi", "GeezaPro", "KohinoorBangla-Regular"
*/
*:not(code):not(h1):not(h2):not(pre):not(kbd):not(icon):not(input):not(button):not(i):not([class*="icon"]):not([class*="fa"]):not([class*="octicon"]):not([class*="win-icon"]):not([class*="icon-"]):not([class*="ace_"]):not([class*="ico"]):not([class*="pc"]):not([class*="DPvwYc"]):not([class*="para"]):not([class*="ms-Icon"]):not([class*="sort-caret"]):not([class*="Da"]):not([class*="drop"]):not([class*="bowtie-"]):not([class*="view-"]):not([class*="pl-"]):not([class*="avatar-"]):not([class*='wysiwyg-macro-*']) {
    font-family: "Titillium", "Gisha", "Candara", ".AppleSystemFallback-Regular";
    /*font-size: 16px*/
    font-size: 100%;
}
